title: Perfect Blind - Edge Of Solitude
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Five years after his latest album, Perfect Blind is ready to present the new production and fresh music, discovering different aspects of downtempo and ambient music, but all tied up with interesting storytelling and top notch production. Download Wanderers - http://www.neogoa.net/wanderers/

Tracklist:

01 - Passing The Veil (0 BPM)
02 - Floating Spheres (90 BPM)
03 - Outerland (90 BPM)
04 - Syncope 2015 (95 BPM)
05 - Lunar Dawn - Blessings From Irij [Perfect Blind Remix] (90 BPM)
06 - Edge Of Solitude (0 BPM)
07 - Sabled Sun [feat. Subscale] (100 BPM)
08 - March Of The Dragonflies (100 BPM)
09 - Nephilim' Dance [feat. PsiloCybian] (100 BPM)
10 - Wanderers (85 BPM)
